# Private dashboard exclusion list — NOT exported in plugin bundles.
# Copy this file to ~/.claude/dashboard-filters.local and add patterns you want
# stripped from the dashboard (matched case-insensitively against sender, subject,
# title, and meta fields in gmail/slack/granola agent output).
#
# One pattern per line. Lines starting with `#` are comments. Blank lines ignored.
#
# Examples:
#   some-company
#   personal-project-name
#   some.person@example.com

